        <div class="suds-home-ticker__group">
          <span>Mobile service at home or office</span>
          <span>Basic, Signature, and Elite details</span>
          <span>Ceramic protection available</span>
          <span>Direct communication with Suds</span>
        </div>
        <div class="suds-home-ticker__group" aria-hidden="true">
          <span>Mobile service at home or office</span>
          <span>Basic, Signature, and Elite details</span>
          <span>Ceramic protection available</span>
          <span>Direct communication with Suds</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="suds-home-shell suds-home-dark-proof__intro">
      <h2>Make it shine without leaving home.</h2>
      <p>Suds Auto Salon brings professional mobile detailing to your driveway, office, or approved parking location in the Seattle area.</p>
      <div class="suds-home-dark-media">
        <img src="{{ stock_hero_image }}" loading="lazy" alt="Real hand wash detailing photo with soap on a vehicle window">
      </div>
      <div class="suds-home-actions suds-home-actions--center">
        <a class="suds-home-button suds-home-button--blue" href="{{ booking_url }}">Schedule Your Detail</a>
        <a class="suds-home-button suds-home-button--gray" href="{{ quote_url }}">Request a Quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="suds-home-shell suds-home-gallery-copy">
      <h2>Show your car some love.</h2>
      <p>Cleaner interiors, sharper paint, better wheel presentation, and a vehicle that feels easier to be proud of.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="suds-home-mosaic" aria-label="Suds Auto Salon recent detailing images">
      {%- if has_gallery_blocks -%}
        {%- for block in section.blocks -%}
          {%- if block.type == 'gallery_image' and block.settings.image != blank -%}
            <figure class="suds-home-mosaic__item" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
              {{ block.settings.image | image_url: width: 900 | image_tag: loading: 'lazy', widths: '360, 540, 720, 900', sizes: '(min-width: 990px) 25vw, 50vw', alt: block.settings.alt_text }}
            </figure>
          {%- endif -%}
        {%- endfor -%}
      {%- else -%}
        <figure class="suds-home-mosaic__item"><img src="{{ stock_basic_image }}" loading="lazy" alt="Professional vehicle wash prep photo"></figure>
        <figure class="suds-home-mosaic__item suds-home-mosaic__item--wide"><img src="{{ stock_signature_image }}" loading="lazy" alt="Foam hand wash on a dark vehicle window"></figure>
        <figure class="suds-home-mosaic__item"><img src="{{ stock_elite_image }}" loading="lazy" alt="Brush detailing around a vehicle headlight"></figure>
        <figure class="suds-home-mosaic__item suds-home-mosaic__item--tall"><img src="{{ stock_coating_image }}" loading="lazy" alt="Glossy paint reflection on a clean black vehicle"></figure>
        <figure class="suds-home-mosaic__item"><img src="{{ stock_vehicle_image }}" loading="lazy" alt="Clean dark vehicle interior detail photo"></figure>
      {%- endif -%}
    </div>

    <div class="suds-home-shell suds-home-wash-compare">
      <h2>Car Wash vs. A Real Detail</h2>
      <p>A car wash hits the surface. A real detail addresses the buildup that comes from driving: interior grime, dust, crumbs, body oils, road film, dirty wheels, contaminated paint, and tired finishes.</p>
      <a class="suds-home-button suds-home-button--gold" href="#packages">Choose a Detail</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="suds-home-why">
    <div class="suds-home-shell">
